Usage<br/><br/>
hold (item)<br/><br/>
<br/>
Lets you hold an item in the hand. This is used for wands wands and<br/>
staves. To use such an item you must hold it in your hand. It is possible<br/>
to hold an item in one hand, and wield a singlehanded<br/>
weapon in another.<br/>
