Sphere: Creation Sphere<br/><br/><br/>
<br/>
Usage cast hold (target)<br/><br/>
<br/>
The hold spell will magically prevent a humanoid or animal target from<br/>
engaging in combat for five rounds.  This spell is very difficult to use,<br/>
and may therefore fail quite often.<br/>
